  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43084</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_087_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あの仮面の人たち、
何したいんだろ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Those Masked people... I wonder what they're up to.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43156</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_087_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>単なる嫌がらせだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Simply being a pain in the ass, that's what.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43256</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_087_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でもどうして、嫌がらせなんて
する必要があるの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...why would they feel they need to do these bad things in the first place?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43336</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_087_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どこかでなんかの恨み買った？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Perhaps they hold a grudge against us?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43432</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_087_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今までわたしたち、
家出たことなかったのに？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Until now they've been convincing us to stay home. Maybe that's it?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43512</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_087_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>顔見ただけでむかついたとかさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I get so angry whenever they show up!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43632</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_087_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ぼくのかわいい双子ちゃんたちは、
そんなむかつく顔なんてしてないよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>My fair pair of twins shouldn't get angry just seeing someone's face!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43728</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_087_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あっちの方がよっぽど、
むかつく顔してるっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They've done so many things to us all I'm also irritated just looking at their faces!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_087_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>顔って……あいつら顔隠してるだろ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Their faces...? But they are wearing masks...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_087_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>大体、なんで顔隠してるの？
あの人たち、誰なの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>For starters, why do they hide their faces? Just who are they?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44012</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_087_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あんなもんひっぺがして、
全部喋らせようぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm gonna rip those masks offa their faces and we'll have a long, sweet talk.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
